'''麦迪逊一号'''（{{lang-en|'''One Madison'''}}）是位于纽约[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]的一栋高档住宅公寓，位于23街，介于[[百老汇|百老汇]]和公园大道南，[[麦迪逊大街|麦迪逊大街]]尽头。建筑大厅在建成后地址为东22街23号。

2010年4月，该建筑已经封顶，但是由于财务危机无法完工。住宅单元的销售停止，但在4月15日于接管者的一次会面后销售继续。<ref>{{cite news |title=One Madison Park to Receivership; Flood of Sales to Come? |first=Dana |last=Rubinstein |url=http://www.observer.com/2010/real-estate/hurray-sales-can-resume-one-madison-park-judge-appoints-receiver |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Observer|The New York Observer]] |date=April 16, 2010 |accessdate=2010-05-15 |archive-date=2010-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418040010/http://www.observer.com/2010/real-estate/hurray-sales-can-resume-one-madison-park-judge-appoints-receiver |dead-url=no }}</ref>但之后大楼依然深受财务状况和法律官司困扰，其中包括多起诈骗诉讼和指控，<ref name=shadow>Rubinstein, Dana [http://www.observer.com/2010/real-estate/shadow-boom?page=1 "In the Shadow of the Boom"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.observer.com/2010/real-estate/shadow-boom?page=1 |date=20100416022250 }}, ''[[New_York_Observer|New York Observer]]'' (March 9, 2010)</ref>在2010年6月在债权人要求下被迫走向破产 。<ref name=related>Jones, David. [http://therealdeal.com/blog/2012/04/04/related-settles-majority-of-one-madison-claims-sets-condo-relaunch-for-late-2012/?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+trdnews+%28The+Real+Deal+-+New+York+Real+Estate+News%29%27%3ERelated%20settles%20majority%20of%20One%20Madison%20claims%3C/A%3E%20%5BReal%20Deal%5D%3Cbr%20/%3E%C2%B7%20%3CA%20HREF= "Related settles majority of One Madison claims, sets condo relaunch for late 2012"] ''The Real Deal'' (April 4, 2012)</ref>

